This archive is the fixture project the pyright integration test materializes to
disk. clean.py type-checks; broken.py references an undefined name so pyright
reports one error-severity diagnostic at line 2, column 12. The empty
pyrightconfig.json pins pyright's project root to the fixture directory so it
does not walk up to an ambient configuration.

-- pyrightconfig.json --
{}
-- clean.py --
def add(a: int, b: int) -> int:
    return a + b
-- broken.py --
def broken() -> int:
    return undefined_symbol + 1
